reviewText: outstanding,the tape came quickly and was in the described condition. thank you
I was expecting a CD .I cannot play it
It was a very nice Christmas present for my father. He is up in years and has been blind since his retirement.  I wish he could see it, but he enjoys listening to the music he loves.
I bought this many years ago for my uncle who loved Lawrence Welk. He enjoyed it for many years. He is now deceased.
We worried about the quality of VHS tapes and were pleasantly surprised to find this one good. My Dad loves Lawrence Welk so this was a present for him.
Bought this for my uncle in Delaware.  He's 92 and cannot get enough o Mr. Welk and cast.  Thank goodness for Lawrence Welk.
I really love my tape and play it often.  I now have four Lawrence Welk tapes and just ordered another one.  Great tapes; great service. I am always happy with the service at Amazon.
